Chinese researchers discovered a clear #DNAdamage and associated molecular changes in the body of the Caenorhabditis elegans. 

The team has also screened a radiation-resistant drug. https://t.co/l5UusWTzU1

legacy.full_text:
The first set of images of #Fengyun3F meteorological satellite has been released！

Launched in Aug. 2023, Fengyun-3F is used to take over the morning orbit meteorological operations from #Fengyun3C.
It will launch pilot operation in next March and offer global data services. https://t.co/1bSkEu8gud
